ol.li:
10. A connecting cable, comprising:
a cable for transmitting a signal;
a first connecting tool attached to one end of the cable; and
a second connecting tool attached to the other end of the cable;
at least one of first and second connecting tools being connected in a freely attachable/detachable manner to a receiving tool of a device provided with the receiving tool having a first wireless communication section that performs wireless communication, and having at a position opposite to the first wireless communication section of the receiving tool a second wireless communication section that performs wireless communication with the first wireless communication section.
